reviewText: These two movie are funny, Eddie murphy is so cool. And so it Dan. They make them so worth it.

This combination actually makes sense, although the order is reversed since "Coming to America" has a cameo that makes sense only if "Trading Places" has been watched.  Both are funny and enjoyable, although some scenes might not be appropriate for children.
Anyone who loves Eddie Murphy comedy movies should buy this for their collection. It's a real must - have dvd.
